<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="13Aug1940"><font color="red">13 August 1940</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Jacques Mercanton): we are in the process of asking permission to enter Switzerland &mdash; we, that is, my son with his son (aged eight), I and my wife and my daughter &hellip; I asked the price at Burgh&ouml;lzli, Zurich, where she has once been &hellip; her case is cyclothimia dating from the age of seven and a half </div>
